column1: PUG BLACK GIFTS CANDLE - STANDARD IMAGE
column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesDog Breed GiftsPug Black Gifts Candle - standard image
column4:
Scented gel candle with a Black Pug image.  This candle is available in 4 styles.  A 12oz Jar that is 4-3/4" tall and 3" in diameter that will burn for 75 hours. The 16 ounce jar is 3" x 5 3/4" and will burn for at least 125 hours. The 24 ounce size measures 4" x 5 3/4" and will burn at least 250 hours, and a wine glass that measures 2 3/4" across and stands 7 1/2" tall.  
Simply select the size and your fragrance choice from the pull down menu below. On the 12oz, 16oz and 24oz jars, the lid can also be personalized with 3 lines of text (up to 15 characters per line).
After the candle is done burning, the tile can be removed from the jar and be made into an ornament or refrigerator magnet. The jar can also be reused as a canister for dog treats. 
  Just a little bit of information about the great breed of Pugs!
  Group: toy 
Size Male: 10-11 inches 
Size Female: 10-11 inches 
Hair: fine, smooth, soft, short and glossy 
Colors: Fawn and Black 
Temperament: playfulness, great charm, dignity, and an outgoing, loving disposition 
Official Club: The Pug Dog Club of America 
Fido's Fun Fact: Josephine, wife of Napoleon, used her Pug "Fortune" to carry secret messages under his collar to her husband while she was imprisoned at Les Carmes.

column3: HomeGlass StylesLarge Tri-Colored Jars
column4:
Maximize your burning pleasure with one of our Large Tri Colored Jar Candles. These three-layer candles are our largest jar gel candles, offering 250 hours of burn time and measuring 4 inches in width by 5-3/4 inches in height.
We use a stunning urn style glass jar for these beautiful, colorful candles and fill them with scented candles varieties that complement one another both in terms of their color and their scents. The scents run all the way through each layer, ensuring that the candles will fragrance the air throughout their entire burn time.
Currently, we have eight options available in our Large Tri Colored Jar Candles collection:
From top to bottom in the candle
NEW *** Autumn Harvest – Apple Pie (Gold), Cinnamon (Brown), Pumpkin (Orange) 
Calm – Rose (Light Red), Frankincense (Gold), Bergamot (Smokey Purple)
Earth – Sage & Citrus (Light Olive), Peace (Light Blue), Rain Forest (Light Green)
Fabulous Fruit - Strawberry (Red), Pineapple (Clear), Blue Hawaiian (Tropical Fruit - Blue)
Floral – Freesia (Pink), Jasmine (Light Greenish Yellow), Lilac Bush (Light Purple)
Fresh – Bay Winds (Light Blue), Fresh Air (Light Green), Gulf Breeze (Light Bluish Purple)
Fruit – Pineapple (Light Yellow), Tropical Sun (Bright Blue), Vanilla (Light Gold)
Neapolitan – Strawberry (Light Red), Vanilla (Light Gold), Chocolate (Chocolate Brown)
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesTheme CandlesFlames of Hope Candle 12oz
column4:
BREAST CANCER AWARENESS CANDLE
October is Breast Cancer Awareness Month. I am sure that you are like us and know someone that has been affected by cancer in one way or another. Gellite is offering our Flames Of Hope candle as a way to make a donation towards breast cancer awareness.
$5 from the retail sale of every Flames of Hope candle will be donated to the National Breast Cancer Foundation.
The candle is our 12oz Jar with a heart shaped tile that contains the ribbon shown to the right. Our regular price on a tiled 12oz tiled candle is $20.97 but for this special design, we are offering it at just $20.
Flames of Hope Tile Candle is a 12oz jar and is shown in our lovely pink freesia scent but is also available in our Bay Winds, Bergamot, Coconut Lime, Cotton Blossom, Eucalyptus Spearmint, Gardenia, Peace and Unscented. This candle glass is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high and will burn for over 75 hours.  
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or would like an additional note you can create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid at no additional charge. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Simply add your message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 12oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 75 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.
Also available as a forever candle with a votive glass inside of the main jar, allowing you to burn tea lights forever.  If you choose the forever candle design, you will receive 6 tea lights to go along with the jar giving you 50 to 60 hours of burn time and is an additional $4 charge.

column3: HomeGlass Styles7.5oz Jar Candle with Shells
column4:
Treat yourself or someone that you love to the beauty of the beach with the 7.5 Ounce Shelled Jar Candles! These lovely scented candles are decorated with natural seashells to bring to mind images of the seashore. The design combines one focal shell with smaller shells in an array of colors and sizes with no two of these gel candles ever being exactly the same.
Completely handcrafted, our 7.5 Ounce Shelled Jar Candles measure 2 7/8 inches in diameter by 4 inches high. They boast a remarkably long burn time at 60 hours, and their fragrances remain just as vibrant and pleasing from the first hour of burn until the end of the candle. After you've enjoyed the candle, you can clean out the jar and use it for home storage.
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.

column3: HomeGlass StylesLarge Tri-Colored Holiday Jars
column4:
Triple the fun this holiday season with our wonderful Holiday Tri Color Jar Candles. With these unique scented candles, you can experience three of our most popular holiday candles stacked one on top of the other to provide over 250 hours worth of burn.
The candles come in a straight sided jar with a tapered top and a flat lid. The jar measures 4 inches in diameter and 5-3/4 inches in height and will have a festive tri-color look that will add to your holiday decor. We offer these gel candles in four different varieties:
From top to bottom in the candle
Santa's Socks -  Christmas Tree (Dark Green), Holiday Home (Light Green), Cinnamon Rush (Dark Red)
Holiday Trio - Christmas Tree (Dark Green), Peppermint (Clear), Cinnamon Rush  (Dark Red)
Traditional Trio - Christmas Tree (Dark Green), Frankincense (Gold), Cinnamon Rush (Dark Red)
Classic Trio - Christmas Tree (Dark Green), Bayberry (Light Green), Cinnamon Rush (Dark Red)
You can also personalize a gold label for the lid of the jar with up to 3 lines of text, 15 characters each.  Just enter your information into the Personalized Label area.

column4:

The set contains a trio of round votive gel candles with simple straight sides. Each one will burn for up to 25 hours, and you can even burn more than one at once to create your own fragrance combinations.

column1: ISLAND SUNSET 4 OZ LEAF VOTIVE CANDLE
column3: HomeFragrancesIsland SunsetIsland Sunset 4 oz Leaf Votive Candle
column4:
A trip to paradise!  Island Sunset is a fragrance array of tropical fruits which include:  mandarin, lime, tangerine, kumquat, watermelon, tart green apples, cantaloupe, and honeydew.  The beautiful pastel peach color is a reminder of that picturesque sunset on that perfect day.
Beautify your space with our 4oz Leaf Votive Gel Candles. A lovely choice for spring or autumn, these handmade votive jar candles have a decorative leaf pattern along their sides. When the candles are unlit, the texture adds elegance to the simple votive glass, and when you light the candle, the leaves will throw shadows onto the surrounding area for a beautiful display.
A great choice for use on a bathroom vanity or on the kitchen counter, the votive scented candles measure 2-3/4 inches in diameter and 2-3/4 inches in height. The candle boasts an extraordinary burn time of over 40 hours and has fragrance all the way to the bottom, so you can enjoy a pleasing scent hour after hour.

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesPhoto CandlesPhoto Candle 16oz
column4:
Are you looking for that truly unique gift for that special someone or to commemorate that special occasion?
Look no further.  Gellite Candles Photo candle is your answer.  Simply email us your photo or design and we will create a totally custom photo candle for you using our unique tile candle design.  We will size your image to fit into a 2" circle and will be fired onto a white ceramic disk.  Available in 2 different sizes and over 34 fragrances.
Below you can see an example of how we took a groups logo and created a one of a kind candle to present to their 50 year members in our 16oz Jar Size! To see all sizes of our photo candles, click here photo candles.
Our Photo Tile Candle is a 16oz urn jar currently being shown in our Flower Wreath Tile Candle which is 3 inches across and 5 3/4 inches high.  Photo candles are great gifts for the bridal party, for table centerpieces for either the wedding or for the bridal show, or just as a commemoration of the big day. 
Simply email us the image that you want to use to sales@gellite.com Once we receive your order, we will make up a sample design for you and email it for approval within 2 days.  Once approved, we will make up your custom tile design and your candle.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or would like an additional note for a special occasion, Gellite lets you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Happy Anniversary, Congratulations, or Best Wishes let you really personalized you gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 16oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 125 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column3: HomeGlass StylesBrandy Candle with Shells
column4:
Add elegance and ambiance to any space with our 5oz Brandy Snifter Scented Candles with Shells. These beautiful gel candles are placed in exquisite glass brandy snifters that are 4-1/4 inches high by 2-3/4 inches tall.
A lovely addition to a tablescape, these candles include genuine seashells arranged in a one of a kind oceanscape at the bottom of the glass. Because we use natural materials, no two of these lovely decorative candles are ever the same. column3: HomeGlass Styles16oz Urn Jar Candle
column4:
Love classic wax jar candles with lids? Then, it's time for you to discover our 16 oz Lidded Urn Jar Candles! These beautiful handmade gel candles have a 3 inch diameter and stand at 5 3/4 inches high. Outfitted with a lid just like those wax candles that you love, our jar candles burn for more than 130 hours, giving you much more time to enjoy their light and fragrance than any wax candle. Plus, our scented candles have fragrance all the way to the bottom, so the scent will never run short.
You can choose from a wide array of beautiful smelling and looking varieties for us to pour into this high quality lidded glass jar for your home or business.
Next to the image is a "Personalized Gold Label" option.  Use this to tell us up to 3 lines of 15 characters of text to personalize a gold label for the lid of your candle.  This is a great addition if the candle is being presented as a gift.

column3: HomeFragrancesTropical SunTropical Sun 16oz Urn Jar Candle
column4:
Tropical Sun fragrance is a great combination of lush pineapple and fresh coconut.  We have created this one with a rich blue color that would be the ultimate water color at the beach.
Why not take a mental walk on the beach and picture that warm water lapping at your feet and the warm white sand between your toes.  Smell that aroma of Hawaiian Tropic sun tan location.  That is the essence of our Tropical Sun candles.  This is one of our most popular fragrances both for fragrance and beauty.
This 16oz Lidded Urn Jar is 3 inches in diameter and 5 3/4 inches high. With a burn time of over 125 hours, this beautiful gel candle will provide you many hours of great burning fragrance throughout the life of the candle. These make great gifts and once the candle is complete, the jar can be reused around the house.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, this jar will give you a burn time of over 125 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column4:

column4:
Our 5oz Brandy Glass Candles with Gems are a dazzling, sophisticated twist on classic votive candles. These gel candles come in stunning brandy glasses with tall stems that make them 4-1/4 inches high. Unlike traditional jar candles, the brandy glass candles are raised above the surface upon which they are placed, allowing them to cast a beautiful light display downward.
You can make the effect even more striking by placing the scented candles on a mirror. The 5-ounce size measures 2-3/4 inches in diameter and burns for roughly 45 hours. Traditional and spa scents will feature three gems that match the candle color placed on a bed of sand. The holiday scents include red and green gems on a white salt "snow" base.

column3: HomeGlass Styles5oz Scented Jar Candle
column4:
Interested in trying a new fragrance of scented candles? Our 5 Oz Classic Jar Candles are perfect for sampling a new scent to see how it suits your tastes and how its color complements your decor. These candles measure 2 3/8 inches by 3 1/2 inches in size, so they are compact enough to fit into any area where space is at a minimum. The jar candles also make great stocking stuffers, particularly when you choose to fill them with one of our holiday candles fragrance options.
Popular for use in bathrooms, kitchens and offices, the gel candles burn for more than 50 hours and provide a full, even burn that gives you the most for your money. Because we carefully handcraft our scented candles, the fragrance lasts throughout the life of the candle.
If you are getting this candle for a special occasion or presenting it as a gift, you can create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. column4:

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesPhoto CandlesPhoto Candle 12oz
column4:
Are you looking for that truly unique gift for that special someone or to commemorate that special occasion?
Look no further.  Gellite Candles Photo candle is your answer.  Simply email us your photo or design and we will create a totally custom photo candle for you using our unique tile candle design.  We will size your image to fit into a 2" circle and will be fired onto a white ceramic disk.  Available in 2 different sizes and over 34 fragrances.
Below you can see an example of how we took a groups logo and created a one of a kind candle to present to their 50 year members in our 16oz Jar Size! To see all sizes of our photo candles, click here photo candles.
Our 12oz Custom Photo Tile Candle jar has straight sides and can be made either as a regular candle which will burn for over 75 hours or as a forever candle that will allow you to burn tea lights and even comes with a 6 pack of our 8 to 10 hour tea lights.
Currently show in in our red heart design and our freesia scent. This candle is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high. It will burn for over 75 hours.  These wedding candles are great gifts for the bridal party, for table centerpieces for either the wedding or for the bridal show, or just as a commemoration of the big day. 
Simply email us the image that you want to use to sales@gellite.com Once we receive your order, we will make up a sample design for you and email it for approval within 2 days.  Once approved, we will make up your custom tile design and your candle.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or would like an additional note for a special occasion, Gellite allows you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Happy Birthday, Bon Voyage or Happy Anniversary let you really personalized you gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 12oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 75 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.
This glass style is also available as a forever candle with a votive inside of the main jar, allowing you to burn tea lights forever.  If you choose the forever candle design, you will receive 6 tea lights to go along with the jar giving you 50 to 60 hours of burn time.

A great choice for use on a bathroom vanity or on the kitchen counter, the votive scented candles measure 2-3/4 inches in diameter and 2-3/4 inches in height. Add an eye-catching accent to your decor and fill any room with wonderful fragrance and soft illumination with our 4oz Ice Votive Gel Candles. The look of this exquisite jar candle design was inspired by the frosty look of a block of ice, making it a popular choice for our holiday candles as well as for our scented candles in blue and clear colors. Despite their compact size, these votive candles will burn for more than 40 hours, much longer than wax candles that are identical in size.
The glass container measures 2-3/4 inches across and stands at 2-3/4 inches in height. You're sure to love the long-lasting fragrance of these gel candles and the way the containers create dancing shadows every time the wicks are lit.
Shown in out Tropical Sun, but available in all our great fragrances using the pull down menu.

column3: HomeGlass StylesMartini Gel Candle
column4:
How do you like your scented candles? Shaken not stirred! Our Martini Glass Gel Candles are a clever way to decorate for a cocktail party and also make a great gift for anyone whose signature drink is a classic martini. For this candle, we use a 4-1/2-inch by 7-inch martini glass in place of traditional glass containers used in our jar candles and other styles.
The chic, unique candles will burn for over 65 hours, and we can make them in any of our scented candles varieties. The standard design includes a playful olive accent at the bottom to complete the genuine martini look, but we can eliminate the olive upon request. Just send us a message when you place your order, and we'll be glad to make the change for you.

column3: HomeFragrancesApple Pie7.5oz Jar Candle with Gems
column4:
Add some glitz to your decor with our 7.5oz Scented Jar Candles with Gems. These beautiful handmade gel candles feature three exquisite colored glass gems that are hand selected to ensure quality. The hue of the gems will be selected to coordinate with the color of the scented candles that you opt for when making your purchase. Pick one of our traditional or spa scents, and the gems will be nestled in a bed of sand, or choose one of our holiday candles scents, and we'll add white salt to the jar to create the appearance of snow.
These highly decorative candles make beautiful gifts for the holidays, birthdays, housewarmings and other occasions and can also be used for decorating for parties and special events and you'll be treated to over 65 hours of wonderful fragrance and soft illumination.
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.

column1: STAFFORDSHIRE BULL TERRIER CANDLE BROWN - STANDARD IMAGE
column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesDog Breed GiftsStaffordshire Bull Terrier Candle Brown - standard image
column4:
Scented gel candle with a Brown Staffordshire Bull Terrier image.  This candle is available in 4 styles.  A 12oz Jar that is 4-3/4" tall and 3" in diameter that will burn for 75 hours. The 16 ounce jar is 3" x 5 3/4" and will burn for at least 125 hours. The 24 ounce size measures 4" x 5 3/4" and will burn at least 250 hours, and a wine glass that measures 2 3/4" across and stands 7 1/2" tall.  
Simply select the size and your fragrance choice from the pull down menu below. On the 12oz, 16oz and 24oz jars, the lid can also be personalized with 3 lines of text (up to 15 characters per line).
After the candle is done burning, the tile can be removed from the jar and be made into an ornament or refrigerator magnet. The jar can also be reused as a canister for dog treats. 
  Just a little bit of information about the great breed of Staffordshire Bull Terriers.
  Group: terrier 
Size Male: 14-16 inches 
Size Female: 14-16 inches 
Hair: smooth and short 
Colors: varies 
Temperament: courage with high intelligence 
Official Club: Staffordshire Bull Terrier Club of America 
Fun Fact: authorities generally agree that the breed can be traced back to the mastiff-like dogs through the old bulldog which, when crossed with British terriers, produced the first bull and terriers.

column4:
Christmas Jar Candle is a 16oz urn jar (Currently shown in Santa Design in Cinnamon Rush) which is 3 inches in diameter by 5 3/4 inches high. It will burn for over 125 hours.
All of the images below are available for your candle.  Simply select the name of the design from the drop down menu.

column3: HomeGlass Styles24oz Urn Jar Candle with Shells
column4:
Whether you're looking for beautiful candle gifts or something lovely to add to your own decor, our 24 oz Urn Jar Candles with Shells are the perfect choice. We carefully craft each of these luxurious gel candles by hand, creating a one of a kind oceanscape in the bottom of the glass urn jar. The oceanscape includes large shells in an array of colors and shapes and will look lovely when complemented by the colors of any of our scented candles. We also include a single glass gem to represent beautiful beach glass.
After burning, the candle urns make wonderful lidded storage containers that you can use in the bedroom, bathroom or any other room of the home. Measuring 4 inches in width by 5 3/4 inches in height, the urn candle burns for over 250 hours.

column3: HomeGlass Styles26oz Straight Side Jar Candle
column4:
Love the classic look of traditional jar candles? Our 26oz Straight Jar Candles will let you get that look with all of the benefits of our premium handmade gel candles. This glass container has simple, sleek slides and a removable lid with air tight seal. The diameter of the top of the jar allows it to work with most standard sized candle toppers and lamp shades, and the container is 4 inches wide by 5-3/4 inches high.
Just one of our 26oz Straight Jar Candles will burn for over 250 hours, and our all-the-way-through fragrancing ensures that the scent will be just as strong during Hour 250 as it is during Hour One. These jar candles make great gifts and are available in every one of our fragrances, including our holiday candles scents.
Simply pick your fragrance for your candle from the drop down list and if you are presenting this great candle as a gift, be sure to include a personalized message in the field provided.  We can print up to 3 lines of 15 characters on a gold foil label that will be applied to the lid of the candle to create a unique gift.

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesChristmas CandlesChristmas Candle 12oz
column4:
Christmas Jar Candle is a 12oz urn jar (currently showing in our Holiday Home scent with the Santa 2 tile) which is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high. It will burn for over 75 hours.
All of the images below are available for your candle.  Simply select the name of the design from the drop down menu.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or for a special occasion, Gellite allows you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Merry Christmas, Happy Holidays, or May there be peace on Earth let you really personalized you gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 12oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 75 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.
This is a great gift for any time from Thanksgiving on and will light up your holiday party. Available year round and available in all fragrances, but for Christmas, we have moved Christmas Tree, Holiday Home, Bayberry, Cinnamon Rush, Butter Rum and Frankincense to the top of the good list.

column3: HomeFragrancesChristmas TreeBrandy Christmas Candle with Gems
column4:
Our 5oz Brandy Glass Candles with Gems are a dazzling, sophisticated twist on classic votive candles. These gel candles come in stunning brandy glasses with tall stems that make them 4-1/4 inches high. Unlike traditional jar candles, the brandy glass candles are raised above the surface upon which they are placed, allowing them to cast a beautiful light display downward.
You can make the effect even more striking by placing the scented candles on a mirror. The 5-ounce size measures 2-3/4 inches in diameter and burns for roughly 45 hours. Holiday scents include red and green gems on a white salt "snow" base.
Shown in Holiday Home with Christmas glass gems in red and green.

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesHanukkah CandlesHanukkah Tile Scented Candle 12oz
column4:
Hanukkah Candle 
Hanukkah, also known as the festival of lights, is an eight day holiday commemorating the rededication of the Holy Temple in Jerusalem.  It is observed for eight days and nights. The festival is observed by the lighting of a nine-branched menorah, with one being lit each night.  
Our version of a Hanukkah candle is our 12oz jar candle with a ceramic tile.  We have two images.  One wishes you a Happy Hanukkah with a Star of David.  Our second image is a more traditional menorah design.  The candle shown is in Apple Pie, but is available in any of our more than 44 fragrances.  
Our 12oz candle jar is 4-3/4 inches tall and measures 3 inches in diameter and will burn for aproximately 80 hours.
We also offer a "Personalized Gold Label" option.  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle.

column3: HomeGlass Styles24oz Urn Jar Candle
column4:
On the hunt for large jar candles that will burn evenly and fill your home with a wonderful scent hour after hour after hour? Our 24 Oz Urn Jar Candles are sure to suit your needs in a beautiful way. Handmade, our gel candles outperform wax candles by burning evenly all the way to the bottom of the jar.
With fragrances mixed all the way through the gel, these candles add fragrance to the air throughout their entire 260+ hour burn time. Available in an array of scented candles options that range from fruity to floral to herbaceous to sweet fragrances, these candles come in a variety to suit every taste. We even make holiday candles in this lovely lidded urn jar for festive decorating or gift giving.
Optionally, you can personalize your candle with a gold foil label with up to 3 lines of 15 characters of text.  Simply type your message in the "Personalized Gold Label" field next to the candle picture.  What a great way to present this as a gift.

column3: HomeGlass StylesBeer Mug Candle
column4:
Having a beer-tasting? Hosting an Octoberfest party? Want to give a great gift to a beer lover or home brewer, or want to make your football party or barbecue a little more stylish? Our Beer Mug Gel Candles are the ideal choice for these and many other occasions with their fun beer mug design.
The gel candles measure 2-3/4 inches in width by 5-1/2 inches in height and burn for over 150 hours. At the top of the candle, we place a layer of unscented beeswax to resemble the foamy head of the beer. This can be left off at your request.
To give the jar candles an authentic appearance, we recommend our Cinnamon, Vanilla, Musk or Chocolate scented candles fragrances for use in this glass style.
Please note that the glass style may vary.

column1: TROPICAL SUN 12OZ JAR CANDLE WITH SHELLS
column3: HomeFragrancesTropical SunTropical Sun 12oz Jar Candle with shells
column4:
Tropical Sun fragrance is a great combination of lush pineapple and fresh coconut.  We have created this one with a rich blue color that would be the ultimate water color at the beach.
Why not take a mental walk on the beach and picture that warm water lapping at your feet and the warm white sand between your toes.  Smell that aroma of Hawaiian Tropic sun tan location.  That is the essence of our Tropical Sun candles.  This is one of our most popular fragrances both for fragrance and beauty.
Our 12oz Jar Candle is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high. It will burn for over 75 hours and is available here as a shelled oceanscape.  Also check out our version with no shells for more of a spa or modern look, or with sand and glass gems which work great for holiday themes.
This lovely straight sided jar candle is a great addition to any room and will fill your home with wonderful fragrances.  This size makes a great housewarming gift and is a memorable way to share your love of candles.
The shape and colors of the shells will vary from candle to candle. No two seascapes are ever exactly alike.  As you look around at our candles, you will see our attention to detail.  Every 12oz shelled gel candle oceanscape has 3 main seashells along with a sprinkling of small shells around the floor of the candle.  We even go so far as to include a small glass gem to represent all the great pieces of sea glass that we have found on our beach vacations.
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.

column3: HomeGlass Styles7.5oz Jar Candle
column4:
Looking to enjoy the beautiful color and remarkable fragrance of our gel candles? Our 7.5 Ounce Jar Candles are a lovely choice, as they are free of embellishments to keep the emphasis on color and the beautiful sight of their burn. Whether you choose one of our holiday candles, spa candles or traditional scented candles to fill the jar, you'll be treated to over 65 hours of wonderful fragrance and soft illumination.
The long burn time comes from the unique properties of gel candles, which melt much more slowly than wax-based candle varieties. The 2 7/8 inch by 4 inch glass jar can be rinsed out and used as a storage container once you have completely enjoyed the scented candle of your choice.
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.

column3: HomeFragrancesTropical SunTropical Sun 12oz Jar Candle
column4:
Tropical Sun fragrance is a great combination of lush pineapple and fresh coconut.  We have created this one with a rich blue color that would be the ultimate water color at the beach.
Why not take a mental walk on the beach and picture that warm water lapping at your feet and the warm white sand between your toes.  Smell that aroma of Hawaiian Tropic sun tan location.  That is the essence of our Tropical Sun candles.  This is one of our most popular fragrances both for fragrance and beauty.
Our 12oz Jar Candle is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high. It will burn for over 75 hours and is available here as a shelled oceanscape.  Also check out our version with no shells for more of a spa or modern look, or with sand and glass gems which work great for holiday themes.
This lovely straight sided jar candle is a great addition to any room and will fill your home with wonderful fragrances.  This size makes a great housewarming gift and is a memorable way to share your love of candles.
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, this jar will give you a burn time of over 75 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column3: HomeFragrancesFreesiaFlames of Hope Candle - Freesia
column4:
BREAST CANCER AWARENESS CANDLE
October is Breast Cancer Awareness Month. I am sure that you are like us and know someone that has been affected by cancer in one way or another. Gellite is offering our Flames Of Hope candle as a way to make a donation towards breast cancer awareness.
$5 from the retail sale of every Flames of Hope candle will be donated to the National Breast Cancer Foundation.
The candle is our 12oz Jar with a heart shaped tile that contains the ribbon shown to the right. Our regular price on a tiled 12oz tiled candle is $20.97 but for this special design, we are offering it at just $20.
Flames of Hope Tile Candle is a 12oz jar and is shown in our lovely pink freesia scent.  This candle glass is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high and will burn for over 75 hours.  
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 12oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 75 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column4:

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesPhoto CandlesPhoto Candle 24oz
column4:
Are you looking for that truly unique gift for that special someone or to commemorate that special occasion?
Look no further.  Gellite Candles Photo candle is your answer.  Simply email us your photo or design and we will create a totally custom photo candle for you using our unique tile candle design.  We will size your image to fit into a 2" circle and will be fired onto a white ceramic disk.  Available in more than 40 fragrances.
Below you can see an example of how we took a groups logo and created a one of a kind candle to present to their 50 year members in our 16oz Jar Size! To see all sizes of our photo candles, click here photo candles.
Our Photo Tile Candle is a 24oz urn jar currently being shown in with a Black Labrador image in our Bay Winds scent.  This candle is  which is 4 inches across and 5 3/4 inches high.  Photo candles are great gifts for the bridal party, for table centerpieces for either the wedding or for the bridal shower, or just as a commemoration of the big day. 
Simply email us the image that you want to use to sales@gellite.com Once we receive your order, we will make up a sample design for you and email it for approval within 2 days.  Once approved, we will make up your custom tile design and your candle.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or would like an additional note for a special occasion, Gellite lets you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Happy Anniversary, Congratulations, or Best Wishes let you really personalized you gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 24oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 250 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column4:
Inspired by the relaxing and beautiful scenery of the beach, our 16 oz Lidded Urn Jar Candles with Shells are one of a kind, handmade scented candles that make lovely gifts and are also perfect for enjoying in your own home or business. The base of the jar is filled with three beautiful seashells, which are finished with a single piece of beach glass and a mix of smaller shells. Because we use natural shells in our design, no two of these scented candles are every the same.
Finished with a lid, the jar candle is 3 inches wide by 5 3/4 inches tall, and it will burn for over 125 hours, outlasting standard wax candles of similar size. Pick your favorite for quick delivery right to your door! 
If you are giving this candle as a gift, be sure to fill in the "Personalized Gold Label" option.  We will create a gold foil label just for you and personalize your candle with 3 lines of up to 15 characters each.  Placed on the center of the lid, it will remind the recipient of this great gift, every time they go to light the candle.

column3: HomeGlass StylesTopper (set of 2)
column4:
Candle sticks and candelabras look elegant on a dinner table or in an entryway; however, stick candles burn quickly and can cause a mess when they begin to drip. We created our Candle Stick Toppers to give you all of the long-lasting fragrance and no-mess burning of our gel candles in a form that will fit in nearly all holders that take stick candles.
The toppers have a stunning tapered shape and are outfitted with fluted rubberized tips that allow them to fit securely into the opening of a candle stick. The candles are 3-1/4 inches high with the pegs included, and they measure 2-3/4 inches in diameter. Each one can burn for around 30 hours, and after they are finished you can clean them out and reuse them with our tealights if you wish.
Available in all of our great fragrances, and many people will purchase 2 sets, one in Cinnamon Rush and one in Christmas Tree and then mix and match on their tables.  We also offer these in an unscented version in gold so as not to take away from the wonderful smells of your holiday dinners. If you would like the gold version, just note that in the comments, or unscented is normally clear.

column3: HomeGlass Styles26oz Straight Side Jar Candle with Shells
column4:
Treat yourself to the beauty of a one of a kind ocean scene with our 26oz Straight Jar Candles with Shells. These individually handcrafted jar candles contain an array of large, beautifully detailed natural seashells as well as a single glass gem that represents a piece of sea glass. Smaller shells are added to the bottom along with natural sand for a beautiful effect. Because we use natural materials, each of these scented candles is a unique design that has never been made before and will never be made again.
Featuring straight sides and a removable lid, our 26oz Straight Jar Candles with Shells can be used with most standard candle shades and toppers. The candles measure 4 inches by 5-3/4 inches and burn for over 250 hours.
Simply pick your fragrance for your candle from the drop down list and if you are presenting this great candle as a gift, be sure to include a personalized message in the field provided.  We can print up to 3 lines of 15 characters on a gold foil label that will be applied to the lid of the candle to create a unique gift.

column4:
Strawberry is one of our mouthwatering scents.  You won't believe how true this one is with the great aroma of fresh strawberry jam.  Done in a light red color to be true to the fragrance.

column3: HomeGlass StylesChampagne Glass
column4:
Make your tablescape truly worth of a toast with our Champagne Glass Gel Candles. These scented candles are a sophisticated way to decorate for any special occasion, as the champagne glass shape is synonymous with celebrations! You can also give these Champagne Glass Gel Candles away as wonderful favors for weddings.
The candle glass looks just like a champagne flute with an elongated bowl that is just 1-1/2 inches wide. Positioned on a sleek stem, the candle stands at 7 inches in height.
We can create these gel candles in any of our fragrances; however, our Champagne scent is by far the most popular choice. The candles have a 65-hour burn time, so they will last well beyond the end of any event.

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesWeddings and Bridal ShowersWedding Tile Candle 16oz
column4:
Wedding Candle with custom tile is a 16oz urn jar candle (currently being shown in our Flower Wreath Tile Candle) which is 3 inches across and 5 3/4 inches high.  These wedding candles are great gifts for the bridal party, for table centerpieces for either the wedding or for the bridal shower, or just as a commemoration of the big day. 
All of the images below are available for your candle.  Simply select the name of the design from the drop down menu and then complete the field "Your Tile Wording" and we will custom design your tile for you.  Once we receive your order, we will make up a sample design for you and email it for approval within 2 days.  Once approved, we will make up your custom tile design and your candle.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or would like an additional note for a special occasion, Gellite allows you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Happy Anniversary, Congratulations, or Best Wishes let you really personalize your gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 16oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 125 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.
If you are looking for a specific color to match the wedding, just let us know.  We may be able to color the candles for you.  Not all scents lend themselves to going to all colors, but we can work with you to come up with a solution that you will be happy with.

column1: TROPICAL SUN 4 OZ ICE SCENTED VOTIVE CANDLE
column3: HomeFragrancesTropical SunTropical Sun 4 oz Ice Scented Votive Candle
column4:
Tropical Sun is not only popular because of the beautiful turquoise color, but because of the fragrance blend of lush pineapple and fresh coconut.
Add an eye-catching accent to your decor and fill any room with wonderful fragrance and soft illumination with our 4oz Ice Votive Gel Candles. The look of this exquisite jar candle design was inspired by the frosty look of a block of ice, making it a popular choice for our holiday candles as well as for our scented candles in blue and clear colors.
Despite their compact size, these votive candles will burn for more than 40 hours, much longer than wax candles that are identical in size. The glass container measures 2-3/4 inches across and stands at 2-3/4 inches in height. You're sure to love the long-lasting fragrance of these gel candles and the way the containers create dancing shadows every time the wicks are lit.

column3: HomeGlass StylesTea Lights
column4:
Our tiny Tea Light Gel Candles are petite and sweet, but they will fill your room with fragrance in a great big way! These scented candles are highly versatile and can be used in many different types of tea light holders and votive holders within your home.
You can also display them on their own and let their simple containers take center stage. Try placing a group of the tea lights on a mirror for a dazzling effect or purchase one of our heart shape bowls to create your own display by selecting "Add a bowl" for just $5 more.
One box contains six of the same scented gel candles, and you can choose any of our fragrances, including our holiday candles. The tea lights burn for 8 to 10 hours and are 1-9/16 inches by 3/4 inch in size.
Shown here is a great way that you can use tea lights to make a beautiful table decoration.  This was done with 2 Island Sunset tea lights and 4 Rose tea lights put into a heart shape bowl.   
If you like to burn tarts, a great idea is to make your own custom fragrance by burning a tea light in one fragrance and the tart in another.
Simply select your fragrance from the drop down menu.

column1: BAY WINDS 24OZ URN JAR CANDLE WITH SHELLS
column3: HomeFragrancesBay WindsBay Winds 24oz Urn Jar Candle with shells
column4:
Bay Winds.....A fresh, breezy scent with a hint of lemon. Created in a lovely pastel blue.
Take a walk on the beach and picture that warm water lapping at your feet and the warm white sand between your toes.  That is the essence of our Bay Winds candles.  This is one of our most popular fragrances both for fragrance and beauty.
  Our longest lasting urn jar is our 26oz. It will burn for over 250 hours and is 4 inches wide and 5 3/4 inches high. This size makes a great gift in a super long burning candle design.  By being our largest urn jar, we are able to use some larger showcase shells which really show off in the gel candle designs.
The shape and colors of the shells will vary from candle to candle and no two oceanscapes are the same.  Gellite Gel Candles always goes the extra mile when we are hand crafting our gel candles.  Every candle has a small glass gem to resemble sea glass along with a variety of small shells scattered throughout our sandy bottom.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or for a special occasion, Gellite allows you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Happy Birthday, Bon Voyage or Happy Anniversary let you really personalized you gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, this jar will give you a burn time of over 250 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column3: HomeGlass StylesSnowflake Jar
column4:
Add a touch more wonder to your winter wonderland with our Snowflake Jar Holiday Gel Candles. These scented candles come in decorative jars with a frosty snowflake pattern in white along the sides.
The candle measures 4 inches in diameter and is 4 inches tall and will provide 150 hours of light and wonderful fragrance throughout the holiday season. A wonderful gift for Christmas or to take along to the host or hostess of a holiday party or meal, the jar candles are typically filled with one of our holiday candle scents, such as Christmas Tree, Butter Rum, Holiday Home, Cinnamon Rush or Bayberry but are available in any of our fragrances.
The jar candle includes a domed lid, and after the holiday season has ended, you can clean it and use it as a candy dish.

column1: TROPICAL SUN 16OZ URN JAR CANDLE WITH SHELLS
column3: HomeFragrancesTropical SunTropical Sun 16oz Urn Jar Candle with shells
column4:
Tropical Sun fragrance is a great combination of lush pineapple and fresh coconut.  We have created this one with a rich blue color that would be the ultimate water color at the beach.
Why not take a mental walk on the beach and picture that warm water lapping at your feet and the warm white sand between your toes.  Smell that aroma of Hawaiian Tropic sun tan location.  That is the essence of our Tropical Sun candles.  This is one of our most popular fragrances both for fragrance and beauty.
This 16oz Lidded Urn Jar is 3 inches in diameter and 5 3/4 inches high. With a burn time of over 125 hours, this beautiful gel candle will provide you many hours of great burning fragrance throughout the life of the candle. These make great gifts and once the candle is complete, the jar can be reused around the house.
Gellite Gel Candles prides itself on going the extra step in our candle production.  From the personalized gold label option where you can add up to 3 lines of 15 characters to the lid of your jar candle, to the fact that every 16oz shelled gel candle features 3 different larger shells with a number of small shells spread around the sand to resemble the beach right at the point where the waves gently move the sand and reveal the beautiful natural sea shells.  We even represent a small piece of beach glass also know as a mermaid tear with a glass gem place within the candle. 
Please note that the shape and colors of the shells will vary from candle to candle. No two seascapes are ever exactly alike.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, this jar will give you a burn time of over 125 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column1: STRAWBERRY 16OZ URN JAR CANDLE WITH SHELLS
column3: HomeFragrancesStrawberryStrawberry 16oz Urn Jar Candle with shells
column4:
Strawberry is one of our mouthwatering scents.  You won't believe how true this one is with the great aroma of fresh strawberry jam.  Done in a light red color to be true to the fragrance.
This 16oz Lidded Urn Jar is 3 inches in diameter and 5 3/4 inches high. With a burn time of over 125 hours, this beautiful gel candle will provide you many hours of great burning fragrance throughout the life of the candle. These make great gifts and once the candle is complete, the jar can be reused around the house.
Gellite Gel Candles prides itself on going the extra step in our candle production.  From the personalized gold label option where you can add up to 3 lines of 15 characters to the lid of your jar candle, to the fact that every 16oz shelled gel candle features 3 different larger shells with a number of small shells spread around the sand to resemble the beach right at the point where the waves gently move the sand and reveal the beautiful natural sea shells.  We even represent a small piece of beach glass also know as a mermaid tear with a glass gem place within the candle. 
Please note that the shape and colors of the shells will vary from candle to candle. No two seascapes are ever exactly alike.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, this jar will give you a burn time of over 125 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.

column3: HomeSpecialty & AccessoriesWeddings and Bridal ShowersWedding Tile Candle 12oz
column4:
Wedding Candle with custom tile is a 12oz jar and is currently shown in in our red heart design and our freesia scent. This candle is 3 inches in diameter by 4 3/4 inches high. It will burn for over 75 hours.  These wedding candles are great gifts for the bridal party, for table centerpieces for either the wedding or for the bridal shower, or just as a commemoration of the big day. 
All of the images below are available for your candle.  Simply select the name of the design from the drop down menu and then complete the field "Your Tile Wording" and we will custom design your tile for you.  Once we receive your order, we will make up a sample design for you and email it for approval within 2 days.  Once approved, we will make up your custom tile design and your candle.
If you are presenting this candle as a gift or would like an additional note for a special occasion, Gellite allows you to create a personalized gold foil label that will be centered on the lid. There is room for up to 3 lines of 15 characters each. Things like Happy Birthday, Bon Voyage or Happy Anniversary let you really personalize your gel candle.  Simply add your personal message in the area that says "Personalized Gold Label" before you add the item to your cart.
Since gel candles last much longer than regular wax candles, the 12oz jar will give you a burn time that exceeds 75 hours and the fragrance will last throughout the life of the candle.
If you are looking for a specific color to match the wedding, just let us know.  We may be able to color the candles for you.  Not all scents lend themselves to going to all colors, but we can work with you to come up with a solution that you will be happy with. 
This glass style is also available as a forever candle with a votive inside of the main jar, allowing you to burn tea lights after the candles initial burn and keep your design "forever".  If you choose the forever candle design, you will receive 6 tea lights to go along with the jar giving you 50 to 60 hours of burn time.

column3: HomeGlass StylesMoonshine Candle
column4:
Nothing says it's a party more than a Moonshine Candle.  This addition to the drink line of our scented gel candles is sure to be a hit with the redneck side of your social calendar.
Moonshine is one of the fastest growing spirits in the US and has come a long way from the illegal distillaries of appalacia in the 1800's.  We thought that it was interesting that Moonshine is really just unaged, white whiskey!  
While many brands of moonshine are served in ball mason jars, we have added a twist by making our moonshine candle in a mason jar with a handle. This scented gel candle measures 2-3/4 inches in width by 5-1/2 inches in height and burn for over 120 hours. 
To give the moonshine candles an authentic appearance, we recommend our clear scents including Citrus Blast,  cotton blossom, gardenia, and vanilla coconut.  But as is true with almost all of our Gellite candles, the choice is yours, just remember the scent you choose affects the color and the candle color is listed after the scent name in the drop down menu .
Please note that the glass style may vary.
If you wanted to learn a little more about the business of moonshine in the US, check out this article from Time "Moonshine is growing"

column3: HomeGlass Styles12oz Jar Candle with Shells
column4:
Our 12oz Shelled Jar Candles are lovingly made to capture the beauty of the seashore while treating you to the wonderful fragrance of one of our scented candles. This size of jar candle s 4-3/4 inches tall and measures 3 inches in diameter. When you study the details of the oceanscape in the bottom of the jar, you'll find three large seashells, an assortment of smaller shells and a single glass gem. No two of the designs are ever identical, making each one a new experience for your home.
Also a wonderful choice for a housewarming or host or hostess gift, the candle burns for more than 75 hours, and the glass jar can be reused as a decorative item or a storage container. 
Notice the "Personalized Gold Label" option?  Just tell us what you want the top of your candle to say and we will personalize it for you with up to 3 lines of 15 characters each.  What a great way to add a personalized message to the recipient of the candle, or as a way to commemorate a special occasion.
